fulltitle: This Show is a Nightmare - A Choir Musical
title: This Show is a Nightmare - A Choir Musical
_filename: B:\Projects\maude\Choir\This Show is a Nightmare - A Choir Musical.mp4
description:
Performed at Maude Night 08/01/16 @ UCB Chelsea

Directed by Eric Gersen
Music composed and performed by Eric Gersen

Written by Jenny Huftalen, Jason Sweeten, Benjamin Korman, Michael Romanos, and Kristen Cignavitch

Performed by Colin Marsh, Anna Callegari, Matt Rogers, Sarah Grace Welbourn, and Desi Domo.


Song List:

00:00 "Opening Number"
2:41 "Ghosted Every Dude Here"
6:21 "Teeth Instead of Arms"
9:35 "They Like Me Too Much (The Founding Fathers Song)"
15:04 "Giving Birth to Things That Scare Me"
19:13 "Stay Put (Bigfoot)"
24:38 "Every Dream is Dicks"

Filmed by Lou Gonzalez
